166
00:11:04.958 --> 00:11:06.375  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Bana öyle görünmedi.

167
00:11:06.458 --> 00:11:09.542  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Yani evet, Phil'in bacağının biraz...

168
00:11:10.333 --> 00:11:11.458  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
