226
00:14:15.083 --> 00:14:18.333  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Çalışan bir kadın olmanın telaşesinde

227
00:14:18.417 --> 00:14:20.458  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
